OL,5, Theatre directors would not accept     
OL,6, someone like me now, Sir Mark Rylance  
OL,7, has said.                              
OL,9,FReflecting on how he would be received 
OL,10,Fin today's industry, Sir Mark said     
OL,11,Facting used to be more accepting of    
OL,12,F"oddballs" like him.                   
OL,14,FWhile directors "understandably" want  
OL,15,Factors who are "easy to work with", it 
OL,16,Fcan "also be a loss", he told the BBC's
OL,17,FLaura Kuenssberg.                      
OL,19,FSir Mark was knighted for his services 
OL,20,Fto theatre in 2017.                    
